# Micro Manager

<a style="text-decoration: none" href="https://github.com/precice/micro-manager/blob/develop/LICENSE" target="_blank">
    <img src="https://img.shields.io/github/license/precice/micro-manager.svg" alt="GNU LGPL license">
</a>

